  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Received a Medtronic implantable cardioverter defibrillator (ICD) at Yale
             Electrophysiology, between January 2007 and June 2012

          -  ICD is compatible with Carelink, Medtronic's remote monitoring system

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Less than 18 years of age

          -  From a vulnerable population

          -  Incompetent/suffers from dementia

          -  Non-English speaking
      </textblock>
